title: Am I The A*Hole? She’s 18yrs Old And Making Her Parents Pay Rent?!
description:
She’s turning 18 years old, doesn’t have a job and she’s not in college. Her stepdad recently asked her to pay rent but didn’t know that the house is an inheritance from her late father that now belongs to her. Now, she wants him to pay rent!
